...dan 100 ml Propranolol
dengan interval 8 jam.

146
00:10:27,100 --> 00:10:30,060
– Ya, Dokter.
– Dokter Joo.

147
00:10:32,980 --> 00:10:34,380
Permisi.

148
00:10:40,060 --> 00:10:41,460
Separah apa itu?

149
