operasi itu.

185
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:39,540
Ya, Pak.

186
00:12:40,620 --> 00:12:42,900
Aku mengerti.

187
00:12:47,060 --> 00:12:49,100
Dokter Han, dasar menyebalkan.

188
00:12:50,540 --> 00:12:52,660
Aku tak mengira
dia akan menemui Ketua.

189
00:12:53,980 --> 00:12:57,140
